{"tid":2363923,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"清水健拍AV自備Condom 公開一炮過用量嚇呆網民","createTime":"2021-01-12T14:37:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T18:00:21.000Z","uid":16659,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a4d0a7c102c335eaa5b8f00ca5d183518d5b4f7b","tid":2363923,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T14:37:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/pWgGQTHRgluQc2EH51AKi0SydIE=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DBSZV45YV5GVFHPIHQ6SO6JI2Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FpWgGQTHRgluQc2EH51AKi0SydIE%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDBSZV45YV5GVFHPIHQ6SO6JI2Q.jpg&h=d20c4f56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本AV界天王清水健，於2018年夏天展開人生新一頁，他與女作家伊藤春香（Hachu）組織幸福家庭，兩人在翌年9月榮升父母，令這位愛情動作片首席男優搖身變成一位慈父。<br />\n<br />\n清水健由AV圈踩入不同範疇吸金，更活躍社交網充當性專家。昨晚，清水健在Twitter分享照片，拍下開工時採用的保險套，並寫：「拍攝AV時用的Condom，由我自己貼錢，金額不菲呢。」由於份量多達42盒，故po文出街後，即引起大批網民感到好奇，紛紛留言詢問「是否一次份量？」、「每次要用幾多個？」、「戴上0.01演出時有沒有破爛的經驗？」等等，可見網民對AV行業深感興趣。<br />\n<br />\n清水健最近推出新書《AV男優有可觀收入嗎？》，展現鏡頭後的另一面，並分享當男優的條件及辛酸，是AV界入門天書。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/A63-hmvsSx9K56HEiJOmBQMO3WQ=/802x997/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/47NDVN2BM5HXLBMIE4S2EMYPSE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FA63-hmvsSx9K56HEiJOmBQMO3WQ%3D%2F802x997%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F47NDVN2BM5HXLBMIE4S2EMYPSE.jpg&h=8a0344dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/LszKYX3GWaDAC6nPBT3AbKlqH3M=/802x1069/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DYWG37ZBMNDSXCYKE4S2CGHFOM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FLszKYX3GWaDAC6nPBT3AbKlqH3M%3D%2F802x1069%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDYWG37ZBMNDSXCYKE4S2CGHFOM.jpg&h=7b6774dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JVv2-lPbMXMwi_41Jm23rh8seuc=/802x1150/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TMVUDOMQXVAGLEGADGYGJLC7NE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJVv2-lPbMXMwi_41Jm23rh8seuc%3D%2F802x1150%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTMVUDOMQXVAGLEGADGYGJLC7NE.jpg&h=ea662a35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/0X3jcglgflU8mFZQpTtklCoUK6w=/802x1069/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZGLUU3H7MBCKJLTOPT2ENR6MJM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F0X3jcglgflU8mFZQpTtklCoUK6w%3D%2F802x1069%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZGLUU3H7MBCKJLTOPT2ENR6MJM.jpg&h=b8e6613b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"efb26f8077696b4808c8e9a784e0f4f4900c0d5a","tid":2363923,"uid":151534,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T14:40:54.000Z","msg":"乜閪都插過晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cc2a283be5d65198e11a692eecfb3c435dba320","tid":2363923,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"efb26f8077696b4808c8e9a784e0f4f4900c0d5a","tid":2363923,"uid":151534,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T14:40:54.000Z","msg":"乜閪都插過晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T14:41:27.000Z","msg":"連男人"},{"pid":"9eeda540750452db4a0d521b61a806b415faa33b","tid":2363923,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,